Strings
Concat: {{ concat 1 2 " " "hello" " " "world!" }}
Trim: {{ trim " hello " "   text" "text  " }}

How to use brackets in code:
With concat: {{ concat "}" "}" }}
Shorter version: {{ $} }}
{{ concat "{{ hello " $} }}

How to use double quotes in code:
{{ $quote }}
{{ concat "Hello " $quote "world" $quote "!" }}

Math
Plus: {{ + 1 2 3.3 }}
Plus (concat): {{ + 1 2 "abc" 3 }}
Minus: {{ - 8.3 1 1.4 }}
Multiply: {{ * 4 2 7.2 }}
Divide: {{ / 1440 8 6 4 }}
Modulo: {{ mod 7 4 }}